@startuml
title Component Architecture - E-Commerce System

' Skinparam for professional look
skinparam componentStyle uml2
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Entry Point / Orchestration" {
    [ECommerceSystem] as ECS <<Facade>>
}

package "Product & Inventory Layer" {
    [ProductCatalog] as PC
    [InventoryManager] as IM
}

package "Business Logic Layer" {
    [CartManager] as CM
    [ShippingManager] as SM
}

package "Infrastructure Layer" {
    [PaymentProcessor] as PP
    [NotificationManager] as NM
}

' Defining the Dependency Flow
note top of ECS : Central Hub for Order Processing

ECS --> PC : 1. Queries Product Info
ECS --> IM : 2. Checks/Updates Stock
ECS --> SM : 3. Calculates Shipping
ECS --> PP : 4. Processes Payment
ECS --> NM : 5. Sends Confirmation

' Secondary interactions
IM ..> PC : References Product Data
CM ..> PC : Holds Product Items

@enduml